<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="{{#if lang}}{{lang}}{{else}}fr{{/if}}">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <title>{{#eq lang "en"}}FASO ADMIN — Role granted{{else}}FASO ADMIN — Rôle accordé{{/eq}}</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f3f6f4;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#f3f6f4;padding:32px 0;">
    <tr><td align="center">
      <table width="640" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#ffffff;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#1b5e20;color:#ffffff;padding:28px 32px;">
            <h1 style="margin:0;font-size:22px;">FASO ADMIN</h1>
            <p style="margin:6px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#FFD700;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}Role assignment{{else}}Attribution de rôle{{/eq}}
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:32px;color:#222;">
            <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.55;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}A new role has been granted to your administrator account:{{else}}Un nouveau rôle vient d'être attribué à votre compte administrateur :{{/eq}}
            </p>
            <table width="100%" style="margin:20px 0;border-collapse:collapse;">
              <tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:13px;color:#666;width:35%;">
                {{#eq lang "en"}}Role{{else}}Rôle{{/eq}}
              </td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:14px;">
                <span style="background:#FFD700;color:#1b5e20;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:4px;font-weight:bold;">{{targetRole}}</span>
              </td></tr>
              <tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:13px;color:#666;">
                {{#eq lang "en"}}Granted by{{else}}Accordé par{{/eq}}
              </td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:14px;">{{grantor}}</td></tr>
              <tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:13px;color:#666;">
                {{#eq lang "en"}}Scope{{else}}Périmètre{{/eq}}
              </td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:14px;"><code>{{scope}}</code></td></tr>
              <tr><td style="padding:10px;font-size:13px;color:#666;vertical-align:top;">
                {{#eq lang "en"}}Justification{{else}}Justification{{/eq}}
              </td><td style="padding:10px;font-size:14px;font-style:italic;color:#444;">{{justification}}</td></tr>
            </table>
            <p style="font-size:13px;color:#555;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}Reminder: every admin action is audited (Loi 010-2004) and your operations are traceable.{{else}}Rappel : toutes les actions administrateur sont auditées (Loi 010-2004) et vos opérations sont traçables.{{/eq}}
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#1b5e20;color:#FFD700;padding:14px 32px;font-size:12px;text-align:center;">
            FASO DIGITALISATION — République du Burkina Faso<br/>
            <a href="https://faso.bf/security" style="color:#FFD700;text-decoration:underline;">https://faso.bf/security</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td></tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
